### NestJS API 测试文件
### 使用 VSCode REST Client 插件运行

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3090
@token = your-access-token-here

### ============================================
### 认证模块 (Auth)
### ============================================

### 1. 用户登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 2. 获取当前用户信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 用户模块 (Users)
### ============================================

### 3. 创建用户
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "nickname": "测试用户",
  "password": "test123456",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "status": true,
  "remark": "测试账号"
}

### 4. 获取用户列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. 分页查询用户
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users?page=1&limit=10&username=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. 获取用户详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. 更新用户信息
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "新昵称",
  "email": "newemail@example.com"
}

### 8. 删除用户
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/users/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 角色模块 (Roles)
### ============================================

### 9. 创建角色
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleName": "管理员",
  "roleAuth": "admin",
  "perms": ["user:create", "user:update", "user:delete", "user:export"],
  "status": true,
  "remark": "系统管理员"
}

### 10. 获取角色列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/roles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11. 获取角色详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12. 更新角色
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roleName": "超级管理员",
  "perms": ["*:*"]
}

### 13. 删除角色
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/roles/{{roleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 权限模块 (Permissions)
### ============================================

### 14. 创建权限
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "用户管理",
  "key": "user",
  "parent_key": null,
  "auth": false,
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "status": true
}

### 15. 创建子权限
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "创建用户",
  "key": "user:create",
  "parent_key": "user",
  "auth": true,
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "status": true
}

### 16. 获取权限列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/permissions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 17. 获取权限树
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/permissions/tree
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 18. 获取权限详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 19. 更新权限
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "用户管理模块",
  "sortOrder": 2
}

### 20. 删除权限
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/permissions/{{permissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 操作日志模块 (UsersOptLogs)
### ============================================

### 21. 创建操作日志
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-opt-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operator": "admin",
  "operatorId": "{{userId}}",
  "module": "用户管理",
  "platform": "desktop",
  "operatorIP": "192.168.1.1",
  "address": "中国-北京",
  "content": "创建了新用户"
}

### 22. 获取操作日志列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-opt-logs
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 23. 分页查询日志
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-opt-logs?page=1&limit=20&operator=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 24. 获取日志详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-opt-logs/{{logId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 25. 删除日志
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-opt-logs/{{logId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 文件上传模块 (Upload)
### ============================================

### 26. 上传单个文件
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/upload/single
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="test.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/test.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### 27. 上传多个文件
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/upload/multiple
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="test1.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/test1.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="files"; filename="test2.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-files/test2.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### ============================================
### 增强版用户模块 (Users Enhanced)
### ============================================

### 28. 创建用户（带权限控制）
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-enhanced
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "newuser",
  "nickname": "新用户",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "status": true
}

### 29. 分页查询用户（增强版）
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-enhanced?page=1&limit=10&username=admin&status=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 30. 导出用户数据为 Excel
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-enhanced/export
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 31. 下载用户导入模板
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-enhanced/template
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 32. 更新用户（带权限控制）
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-enhanced/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "更新后的昵称"
}

### 33. 删除用户（仅管理员）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/v1/users-enhanced/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ============================================
### 健康检查
### ============================================

### 34. 检查服务状态
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### ============================================
### 变量说明
### ============================================
# @baseUrl - API 基础地址
# @token - JWT 访问令牌（从登录接口获取）
# {{userId}} - 用户ID（替换为实际的用户ID）
# {{roleId}} - 角色ID（替换为实际的角色ID）
# {{permissionId}} - 权限ID（替换为实际的权限ID）
# {{logId}} - 日志ID（替换为实际的日志ID）
